The code should now compile and work on NetBSD

Run make clean ; make from the root.

The Makefile will automatically run gmake in the relevant directories

Requires the SDL2 pkg as well as libX11

If you get an error about not being able to init the video make sure you've installed all the dependencies listed here

http://ftp.netbsd.org/pub/pkgsrc/current/pkgsrc/devel/SDL2/README.html
